"Youtube Summary by ChatGPT" is a utility that allows users to summarize video content on YouTube supporting Chrome and other browsers that share the Chromium kernel. It helps to quickly capture very long video content, and allows users to see translations into other languages if available.

You just need to open the video and you will see an additional Video Summary section located in the upper right corner.

You can quickly set the language to be translated by opening the utility's popup at any time.
